---
title: Hidden Veggie & Lentil Lasagne with Green Salad & Parmesan
description: Construction is key when making a good lasagne but maybe more importantly is what you pack in. Lay a sheet of lasagne and
begin adding the rich tomato sauce dotted with hidden sautéed veggies. Then another lasagne sheet and more sauce and more
and more! Don’t forget the Parmesan to give it an extra zap.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

